{"tid":1491272,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"危急!!! 我地就黎輸!!! 中共轉左玩法!!!","createTime":"2019-08-20T11:05:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T06:10:50.000Z","uid":61520,"like":191,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"1166e7a0065d24e86659affec9cd3b5c59ee21f2","tid":1491272,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:05:15.000Z","msg":"今日林鄭同黑警開始轉態，加上818五毛全方位轉態，即係中央下達全面指令，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要走懷柔方針，將運動拖入死寂</span></span>，但係唔會回應任何訴求。<br />\n<br />\n亦即係話運動已經進入下場，而現在係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">極危險嘅時刻</span></span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n政府黑警會用盡一切語言偽術、道歉、假拉人、扮溝通、甚至苦肉計黎令事件降溫。黑警尋晚懶理既態度同政府今日完全避開五大訴求嘅行為，好明顯就係佢地無意回應任何訴求。<br />\n<br />\n知己知彼，我地有好多市民出來上街主因係怒氣，對改革嘅追求反而係次要。懷柔方針可能會令好多市民怒氣減退。到時候佢地再陷害我地一劑，就難以返身，變成<span style=\"color: orange;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">雨傘2.0</span></span>。我地會唔會成功，好睇有幾多人會被佢地嘅語言偽術蒙蔽。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n更大嘅一個問題係<span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">五大訴求既文宣嚴重不足</span></strong></span>！！<br />\n已經有幾次有人偷龍轉鳳，<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">將真雙普選偷換成林鄭落台</span></span>！！<br />\n<br />\n所以如果五大訴求非人所佳知，佢地就有機會蒙運過骨！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位手足，每次遊行都要將五大訴求叫出來！每次出黎都要有大banner寫出五大訴求！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">1. 撤回送中惡法<br />\n2. 成立獨立調查委員會<br />\n3. 撤回暴動定性<br />\n4. 釋放所有義士</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">5. 我要真普選</span></span><br />\n<br />\n繼續 和理非&mdash;&gt;死線&mdash;&gt;勇武，是但冇左一樣都會萬劫不復<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">請推以下post<br />\n危急!!! 我地就黎輸!!! 中共轉左玩法!!!<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1491058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1491058</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"da40961d9d8836547fb5266da63a9ec330958852","tid":1491272,"uid":137159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:06:00.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c721ece39e8f90e49f892cad25f12ec73dfd8c6f","tid":1491272,"uid":159596,"like":29,"dislike":0,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:07:23.000Z","msg":"我相信9月會係另一個高潮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n開學<br />\n三罷<br />\n出糧㩒錢<br />\n全部都要做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"58e58d909fe9e19f38a62ea541fa187537359383","tid":1491272,"uid":107297,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:08:08.000Z","msg":"泛民要講明真普選，要引導民氣去真普選"},{"pid":"d71ecb3cbe3d6670f070baeb8dde4f355751fda6","tid":1491272,"uid":83836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:09:37.000Z","msg":"推推推推推<br />\n推爆你"},{"pid":"0640035470fa138d9a36f7234240eadca14eb68e","tid":1491272,"uid":148403,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1166e7a0065d24e86659affec9cd3b5c59ee21f2","tid":1491272,"uid":61520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-20T11:05:15.000